    - rid: 107151359355650075
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650076
          output: 'The merchant may have been an outlander, but it is impossible
            to deny that his ornaments are truly breathtaking. Their modest price
            allowed us to adorn many of our temples, granting us newfound legitimacy
            in the eyes of the populace!

            [Gained 30 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151359355650077
          output: 'What a disgrace! The decorations seemed a bargain, but we should
            have known better... they were of wretched quality! That man has swindled
            us, and reports of broken finery are already pouring in. Worse still,
            accidents have been caused by their collapse. This is the price of trusting
            outlanders!

            [Lost 30 Zeal]

'
